      "description": "Join millions of players in the world\u2019s most satisfying .io game!\n\nPaper.io 2 is a fun multiplayer game built around one simple idea: move across the arena, draw a trail to expand your territory, and capture the zone before an enemy crosses your path. It\u2019s a fast-paced territory capture battle that's easy to learn but hard to master!\n\nSATISFYING DRAWING &amp; ARCADE GAMEPLAY\nExperience the smoothest and most addictive experience in the io games genre. Everything is designed to feel right, from the smooth expansion to the addictive rush of watching your color conquer the entire map.\nPsst\u2014rumor has it something crazy happens if you capture the whole map at once. Think you can pull it off?\n\nFAST-PACED ONLINE MULTIPLAYER\nForget long tutorials and jump straight into the online area. The rules are simple: draw, close, claim. Whether you\u2019re looking for a quick 1-minute match or a deep strategic battle, it fits your schedule perfectly!\n\nCOLLECT &amp; CUSTOMIZE 100+ SKINS\nUnlock a massive library of skins and avatars to personalize your look. Show off your style to friends and rivals as you expand your territory and collect free daily rewards along the way!\n\nSo\u2026 will you play it safe, or are you going for the big steal? Download Paper.io 2 now and join the arena for free!",
